casebody.data:
Michelene CROWLEY, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
MICHIGAN REALTY SOLUTIONS, Defendant-Appellee. SC: 158010
COA: 341722 Supreme Court of Michigan. March 20, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the April 5, 2018 order of the Court of Appeals is considered and, pursuant to MCR 7.305(H)(1), in lieu of granting leave to appeal, we REMAND

this case to the Court of Appeals for consideration as on leave granted.

Viviano, J., would deny leave to appeal.
